{"tid":1768890,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實要賭贏馬會唔難，你掌握到個技巧就得","createTime":"2019-12-04T11:47:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T03:01:06.000Z","uid":150100,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1198b2a3bcc90e991de6842f42d394a812e6eeeb","tid":1768890,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T11:47:30.000Z","msg":"唔駛話完全掌握基本上已經可以贏七輸三<br />\n完全掌握嘅話要贏九輸一根本冇難度<br />\n咁當然啦，要完全掌握其實就唔係講咁易<br />\n途中有啲小挫折就在所難免嘅<br />\n最緊要係反省自己錯啲咩<br />\n點解人贏錢，你輸錢<br />\n之後再檢討下點解自己會捉錯路<br />\n捱過依段之後就係黃金路<br />\n因為你已經有經驗，識捉路<br />\n根本所有馬會開嘅盤你已經可以一眼睇穿<br />\n一啲普通人估唔到嘅你都可以洞察先機<br />\n去到依個階段，你已經可以話完全掌握到個套路，逢賭必贏<br />\n你可能會問<br />\n頭先我唔係話贏九輸一咩<br />\n啱<br />\n嗰個一其實係你發財立品，特登輸返出去，施捨俾馬會，慎防佢執笠<br />\n因為你已經掌握到個套路，贏幾多，輸幾多，由你話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c0260b3c9fb0757fa24b0567eb4b921e8d1df4","tid":1768890,"uid":204943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T11:51:01.000Z","msg":"真，上年聽咗樓主話之後，已經由公屋轉咗住君臨天下 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8a2512a258dd67ad7116946cc0fee0a6721ff7","tid":1768890,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38c0260b3c9fb0757fa24b0567eb4b921e8d1df4","tid":1768890,"uid":204943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T11:51:01.000Z","msg":"真，上年聽咗樓主話之後，已經由公屋轉咗住君臨天下 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces